<section id="about" class="section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <h3>Know About Our Tree: Neem Tree Features</h3>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="feature-item"><h4>Height</h4><p>Grows between 15 to 30 meters tall, with a broad crown.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-item"><h4>Lifespan</h4><p>Can live for 150 to 200 years or more.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-item"><h4>Leaves</h4><p>Compound and pinnate leaves with 8‚Äì19 toothed leaflets, dark green in color.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-item"><h4>Bark</h4><p>Rough, deeply fissured, and dark brown to gray in appearance.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-item"><h4>Flowers & Fruits</h4><p>Produces small, white, fragrant flowers and yellow-green oval drupes, each with a single seed.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
